sub_title: Drilling Supervisor at Canada Association Of Oilwall Drilling Contractors
summary:
I had 27 years experience on Drilling Engineering with several Drilling Companies.
I deal with positions on a variety of installations such as Drillship, Jack Up, Semi submersible, platform & FPSO such as Rig Manager, OIM, Toolpusher, Driller, Barge Engineer, Assistant Driller, Derrickman, Roughneck, Roustabout, Crane Op, Assistant Crane Op, DPO, SDPO, Chief Mechanic, Mechanic, Chief Electrician, Electrician, Motorman, Electronic Technician, Systems Engineer, Materials Co-ordinator / Storekeeper, Radio Operator, HSE / RSTC, Subsea Engineer (MUX and non MUX) and Maintenance Supervisor. These positions can be on cyber or conventional rigs.
I also deal with various onshore Oil & Gas roles.
